@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container">
    <div class="home-content">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
        
        <div class="legal">
            <p class="legal__meta"><strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 21, 2026</p>

            <h2 class="legal__section">Introduction</h2>
            <p>Welcome to pearlxcore.dev ("we," "us," "our," or "Company"). We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.</p>

            <h2 class="legal__section">1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p><strong>Voluntary Information:</strong></p>
            <ul class="legal__list">
                <li>Comments posted on blog articles (via GitHub Utterances)</li>
                <li>Any information you choose to submit through contact forms</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p><strong>Automatically Collected Information:</strong></p>
            <ul class="legal__list">
                <li>Log data (IP address, browser type, pages visited)</li>
                <li>Device information and site usage analytics</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="legal__section">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use collected information for:</p>
            <ul class="legal__list">
                <li>Improving site functionality and user experience</li>
                <li>Responding to inquiries and feedback</li>
                <li>Compliance with legal obligations</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="legal__section">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p><strong>GitHub (Utterances):</strong> Comments are stored as GitHub issues. Your GitHub account information is handled per GitHub's Privacy Policy.</p>

            <h2 class="legal__section">4. Data Security</h2>
            <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the internet is completely secure.</p>

            <h2 class="legal__section">5. Your Rights</h2>
            <p>You have the right to:</p>
            <ul class="legal__list">
                <li>Access your personal information</li>
                <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
                <li>Opt-out of tracking</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="legal__section">6. Cookies</h2>
            <p>Our site may use cookies for authentication and site functionality. You can control cookie settings in your browser preferences.</p>

            <h2 class="legal__section">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p>We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13. If we become aware of such collection, we will delete this information promptly.</p>

            <h2 class="legal__section">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last Updated" date.</p>

            <h2 class="legal__section">9. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>For privacy-related questions or concerns, please reach out through our website's contact form or GitHub repository.</p>

            <hr class="legal__divider" />
            <p class="legal__note">By using pearlxcore.dev, you consent to this Privacy Policy.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
